name: Songs From The Road Zine #1
description:
Our first issue of Songs From The Road. It's a zine about culture, music, graphic arts, short stories, poems, ect.

There are 60+ pages and it's only 2 dollars(plus a dollar shipping)

name: Songs From The Road Zine #1(Digital Copy)
description:
Same as the physical copy, minus shipping/printing costs. Free with donation.

We'll send you a PDF file to your email. Include the email address desired with order or we'll send it to your paypal email

name: Donate
description:
Add this to your cart as many times as you'd like.

We are collecting donations to buy a PA Soundsystem. Currently I have to spend 20 dollars out of my pocket in gas to pick one up for every show. It would save me a lot of time and money and my club would greatly appreciate it.

Any help is greatly appreciated. Feel free to order the zine instead for 50 cents if you can't spare a dollar.
